snippet.title: I Created My Own Game Awards 2025 Orchestra Game of the Year Medley
snippet.description:
This medley features the best, most epic themes from the 2025 Game of the Year nominees, including Clair Obscur: Expedition 33, Hollow Knight: Silksong, Hades 2, Death Stranding 2: On the Beach, Kingdom Come: Deliverance II and Donkey Kong Bananza. How do you think I did? Let me know below! No AI used in the music or creation of this Medley. All Music is from the official soundtracks of each game.

Timestamps:

0:00 - Donkey Kong Bananza
0:37 - Death Stranding 2: On the Beach
1:21 - Hades 2
2:05 - Kingdom Come: Deliverance II
2:39 - Hollow Knight: Silksong
3:20 - Clair Obscur: Expedition 33
3:50 - Outro
